query:
INSERT INTO
                    recursion_tip_witness_jobs_fri (
                        l1_batch_number,
                        status,
                        number_of_final_node_jobs,
                        protocol_version,
                        created_at,
                        updated_at,
                        protocol_version_patch
                    )
                VALUES
                    (
                        $1,
                        'waiting_for_proofs',
                        $2,
                        $3,
                        NOW(),
                        NOW(),
                        $4
                    ) ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number) DO
                UPDATE
                SET
                    updated_at = NOW()
